The following article details the Altamaha River.

# Altamaha River

The [Altamaha River](/River) observed from the bridge connecting [Glynn County](/Glynn_County,_Georgia) and [McIntosh County](/McIntosh_County,_Georgia), [Georgia](/Georgia_(U.S._state)), USA.

